episodes.title: 10. From volunteer to cult member: PART 1 | What did she say Podcast
episodes.description:
In this episode, I’m taking you with me to Spain—where I accidentally joined what can only be described as a camp cult. Okay, maybe not a real cult, but when you hear about the chaos… you’ll get it. This is Part One of my two-part diary about the English-speaking Spring camp I volunteered at. From the moment I got the email about this ‘amazing opportunity’ to my very first steps into the world of forced singing, non-stop activities, and zero personal space—this week one recap covers it all. Expect some laughs, culture shock, questionable life choices, and me wondering: why did I do this to myself? Tune in as I spill everything from my first impressions, the bizarre camp rules, and the wild characters I met… and trust me, it only gets worse from here.
